cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DS

This paper proposes a metric learning approach for distance-based classification in time series. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
